-01T20:40:06.000Z","msg":"連登仔乜人都屌架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c98238ec0339ab07dfb3a6a2f6b9e2bcb7a5fb9d","tid":2349783,"uid":284432,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T20:42:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a6c4320b220d20af32c52d51a4205c734d6ce007","tid":2349783,"uid":370010,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T20:58:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5f7bdc91cda0f5e5bdc57748d12d3724c7e7065d","tid":2349783,"uid":225846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T22:22:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a8aac35b06a0e7addf9cb9f9f1c042ed16df5e57","tid":2349783,"uid":59570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T22:25:28.000Z","msg":"拜金冇問題<br />\n<br />\n你要做物質奴隸點解要阻你啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2b9c4b4652c516f7dae7e1250707e2dfc7e905c","tid":2349783,"uid":41988,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T22:38:25.000Z","msg":"咁拜登呢"},{"pid":"c5e7b60c88f2d61768354ad084aeb52810748758","tid":2349783,"uid":39376,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T23:13:58.000Z","msg":"拜金無問題呀，以前有個朋友好拜金，為左釣有錢佬去做雞添<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />不過良禽擇木而棲，我覺得拜金既人多數會鄙視窮撚，咁樣既人思想好狹窄"}]}